Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.17,0:00:03.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发现入侵者
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.36,0:00:04.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还击
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.99,0:00:05.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保卫乌尔班
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.63,0:00:17.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘘
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.20,0:00:20.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.55,0:00:21.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪奥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.17,0:00:25.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,联邦的暗杀部队已经
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.30,0:00:28.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃离安那托勒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.94,0:00:46.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是阴魂不散
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.35,0:02:47.93,NOTE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Block\N————\N国际象棋棋题的一种。\N该棋题中当黑方下出解题的第一着后、白方的后着并不会给黑方带来威胁。\N但黑方反而会将自己置于强制被动的局面下。\N该情况下无论黑方怎样行动都会被将死。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.54,0:03:18.09,Gurakiesu,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你醒了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.88,0:03:20.84,Gurakiesu,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你睡了一整天
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.18,0:03:24.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.97,0:03:27.51,Gurakiesu,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明身在敌营…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.68,0:03:29.31,Gurakiesu,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却丝毫也不紧张
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.04,0:03:31.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉泽和米莉娅呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.32,0:03:36.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有没有看到两个女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.75,0:03:42.20,Gurakiesu,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她们在山丘上的小屋里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.82,0:03:57.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里在丘尔比斯观山台的北方偏东北方向118哩处
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.49,0:03:59.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经是很北面了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.97,0:04:01.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  这里果然是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.69,0:04:04.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉泽  米莉娅
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.87,0:04:09.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们两个真是担心死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.66,0:04:10.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法姆真是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.11,0:04:12.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你身上不疼了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.10,0:04:13.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.39,0:04:15.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个孩子是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.77,0:04:17.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,语言也不通
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.56,0:04:18.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.55,0:04:22.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是格拉吉艾斯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.46,0:04:25.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.93,0:04:31.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坠落在了格拉吉艾斯国境内
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.19,0:04:39.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你  你太努力了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.43,0:04:42.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能从那枪林弹雨中逃出来真不容易
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.12,0:04:44.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们还活着真不可思议
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.63,0:04:47.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是她救了我们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.84,0:04:49.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.25,0:04:53.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希尔维乌斯成功逃脱了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.73,0:04:56.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修理一下能飞吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.35,0:04:59.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  但损伤得太严重了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.64,0:05:02.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算要修理  也没有零件…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.02,0:05:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.82,0:05:10.83,Gurakiesu,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.12,0:05:13.95,Gurakiesu,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不敢当  只要翼之巫女开口
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.12,0:05:15.62,Gurakiesu,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是外国我们也会去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.83,0:05:17.87,Gurakiesu,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是你交代的蔬菜和衣服…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.96,0:05:21.50,Gurakiesu,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有这是我们给您的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.60,0:05:24.42,Gurakiesu,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢  这是报酬
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.23,0:05:27.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,格拉吉艾斯的人为什么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.17,0:05:30.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子究竟是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.23,0:05:32.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是个大人物吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.87,0:05:35.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对  她带了一群同伙过来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.60,0:05:37.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们要被俘了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.68,0:05:38.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果她真打算这么做的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.14,0:05:41.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得我们早就会被剥个精光了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.12,0:05:43.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.55,0:05:45.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连工具也没有被没收
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.40,0:05:47.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是她可是那个格拉吉艾斯的人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.77,0:05:49.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们说不定会被生吞活剥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.96,0:05:51.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也太夸张了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.04,0:06:11.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您…赐予我等…生命
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.03,0:06:12.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你听的懂吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.41,0:06:13.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.25,0:06:19.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勿忘我之魂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.60,0:06:23.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歌颂吧  感谢苍生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.57,0:06:38.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好香啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.15,0:06:39.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.83,0:06:41.79,Gurakiesu,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是什么人？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.33,0:06:44.54,Gurakiesu,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们为何不先自报家门？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.87,0:06:46.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫米莉娅
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.09,0:06:49.72,Gurakiesu,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米莉娅·伊·威尔克·库特蕾特拉·图兰？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.88,0:06:51.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.20,0:06:53.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一下子就报出了全名
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.68,0:06:56.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我直到现在都记不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.59,0:06:58.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法姆
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.31,0:07:00.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.64,0:07:02.48,Gurakiesu,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮我翻译一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.59,0:07:08.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是保卫国家的翼之巫女
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.04,0:07:10.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前多亏你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.85,0:07:13.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是那个时候的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.02,0:07:17.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要救我的部下？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.84,0:07:21.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要让风来托起迷航的翅膀嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.29,0:07:26.25,Gurakiesu,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若有人困惑于空中  则必定出手相助
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.46,0:07:27.59,Gurakiesu,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是空族的准则
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.21,0:07:29.42,Gurakiesu,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪怕对方是敌人也一样吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.15,0:07:31.22,Gurakiesu,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个老好人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.73,0:07:32.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她说你是个老好人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.59,0:07:34.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不也是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.26,0:07:38.64,Gurakiesu,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想欠外人人情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.52,0:07:40.54,Gurakiesu,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.72,0:07:42.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要翻译吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.18,0:07:44.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大致能猜到什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.22,0:07:53.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薇奥拉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.57,0:07:57.49,Gurakiesu,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来  玛格诺丽雅
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.91,0:07:59.83,Gurakiesu,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一个人吗？  蒂安呢…？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.24,0:08:01.95,Gurakiesu,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她感冒了在睡着
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.83,0:08:05.50,Gurakiesu,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天3点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.17,0:08:08.17,Gurakiesu,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,联邦有所行动
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.62,0:08:15.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰队已在波雷亚斯要塞东北方150哩处不断集结
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.15,0:08:19.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凯范  奥兰  索路修
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.89,0:08:21.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,集结三支舰队的全力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.34,0:08:23.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进攻格拉吉艾斯！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.64,0:08:25.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥古斯塔万岁
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.63,0:08:29.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁来打头阵
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.18,0:08:33.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴托斯  莱图斯  塔·奥比斯丹  凯奥斯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.45,0:08:36.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要让从属国舰队打头阵吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.79,0:08:38.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从属国并不会被抛弃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.13,0:08:41.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了奥古斯塔和臣民们的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.67,0:08:43.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能助我等一臂之力吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.42,0:08:46.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵命  就算粉身碎骨也在所不辞
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.90,0:08:48.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会辜负您的期望
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.46,0:08:51.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是  奥古斯塔万岁
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.63,0:08:54.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥古斯塔万岁
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.63,0:08:56.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.93,0:09:01.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我们齐心协力  夺回我们的故乡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.46,0:09:06.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是至高无上的荣誉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.04,0:09:09.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  这证明奥古斯塔非常信任我们
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.30,0:09:14.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我等凯奥斯遗民团  誓将旗开得胜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.47,0:09:18.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢大家
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.46,0:09:22.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三天后开始进攻格拉吉艾斯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.93,0:09:26.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只为完成自己的使命
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.35,0:09:32.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我并没有原谅你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.30,0:09:34.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.62,0:09:51.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是希尔维乌斯的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.17,0:09:54.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  是舰体操作指南
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.62,0:09:55.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔琪安娜舰长给我的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.98,0:09:59.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泰蒂他们也平安无事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.31,0:10:03.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们一定能再见面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.23,0:10:05.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那还用说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.07,0:10:08.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我在重逢之前要把这本书…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.97,0:10:12.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也和舰长约好了一定会来接我们
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.61,0:10:13.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.41,0:10:14.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.90,0:10:21.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.31,0:10:23.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她让我们用这些来维修先锋艇
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.97,0:10:25.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还说不会通报上级
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.27,0:10:27.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是维修…法姆？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.29,0:10:33.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.70,0:10:36.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.64,0:10:39.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…那个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.55,0:10:42.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢  你听的懂吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.36,0:10:44.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.43,0:10:47.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢  谢  你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.02,0:10:51.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.14,0:10:53.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.63,0:10:58.96,Gurakiesu,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她在向你道谢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.76,0:11:09.68,Gurakiesu,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还缺什么零件跟我说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.02,0:11:11.52,Gurakiesu,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我帮你们准备
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.43,0:11:14.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她好像会帮我们准备机体的零件
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.09,0:11:17.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗  你还真是个好人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.10,0:11:22.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是米莉娅
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.53,0:11:23.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而这位可爱的女孩子是吉泽
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.42,0:11:25.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后我是法姆
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.67,0:11:27.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法…法姆？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.77,0:11:28.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.44,0:11:40.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于走到这一步了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.42,0:11:43.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.49,0:11:45.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有一步之遥了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.43,0:12:07.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来能请你帮忙找来这些吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.04,0:12:14.08,Gurakiesu,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,横梁用材10根…铬钼合金钢管20根
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.48,0:12:27.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.11,0:12:41.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然把胡萝卜给剩下了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.05,0:12:44.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒂安小姐不是说了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.54,0:12:45.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里新鲜蔬菜是很珍贵的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.44,0:12:47.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  张开嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.22,0:12:49.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是煮的我就吃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.18,0:12:52.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我等下吃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.64,0:13:08.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒂安
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.10,0:13:17.31,Gurakiesu,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这先锋艇很少见所以我有点好奇
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.32,0:13:27.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉赛尔  蒂安问有没有风挡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.72,0:13:29.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  风挡是指什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.19,0:13:32.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是指覆盖驾驶席的挡风玻璃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.11,0:13:35.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,装上那种东西岂不就感觉不到风了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.21,0:13:38.54,Gurakiesu,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为那样就感觉不到风了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.87,0:13:42.09,Gurakiesu,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风？真是莫名其妙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.77,0:13:43.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叹什么气嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.15,0:13:46.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么啊  吹吹风不是挺好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.84,0:13:53.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她问武器在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.06,0:13:54.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.96,0:13:57.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  法姆结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.79,0:13:59.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这边也完工了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.45,0:14:03.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在空中飞翔哪会需要什么武器呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.03,0:14:09.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好凉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.74,0:14:16.04,Gurakiesu,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们去泡温泉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.64,0:14:24.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住…住手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.24,0:14:27.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不是因为你不肯脱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.02,0:14:29.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁叫你一直盯着我看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.63,0:14:31.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.62,0:14:33.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好  吉泽  从那边拉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.31,0:14:43.15,Gurakiesu,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒂安大人！！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.44,0:14:47.23,Gurakiesu,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翼之巫女  我们可都靠你了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.80,0:14:57.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都很尊敬你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.69,0:14:58.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真了不起啊  蒂安
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.29,0:15:00.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你受到大家的尊敬呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.00,0:15:02.83,Gurakiesu,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天空…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.34,0:15:07.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天空是战场
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.25,0:15:13.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机体上没有装载武器
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.33,0:15:15.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不计回报地帮助他人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.01,0:15:20.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不明白你们究竟为何而飞翔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.28,0:15:23.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除此之外还有什么理由吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.87,0:15:30.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想飞而已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.93,0:15:32.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞翔不是件很开心的事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.29,0:15:34.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在天空中翻翻跟头
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.36,0:15:36.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和别人比比赛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.02,0:15:42.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她问你这样很开心吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.26,0:15:44.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.33,0:15:47.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒂安也要和我一起参加飞行大赛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.60,0:15:48.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞行大赛！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.53,0:15:51.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞行…大赛？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.40,0:15:53.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  全世界的先锋艇齐聚一堂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.37,0:15:55.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在同一片天空下翱翔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.95,0:16:00.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都尽情欢笑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.60,0:16:03.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞行大赛举行的那天
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.15,0:16:05.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既没有争执也没有战争
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.28,0:16:07.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全世界的人都在笑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.56,0:16:11.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但现在走到哪都在打仗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.34,0:16:13.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我讨厌这种天空
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.77,0:16:14.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要再这样下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.28,0:16:16.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.23,0:16:20.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定要举办飞行大赛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.93,0:16:22.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要让大家充满笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.18,0:16:31.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她说这是徒劳
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.06,0:16:42.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是不祥之兆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.24,0:16:46.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一天的夜里也出现了极光
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.87,0:16:47.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一夜？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.59,0:16:52.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞行大赛的前夜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.74,0:16:57.41,Gurakiesu,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一天…我记忆犹新
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.57,0:17:11.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时起  我们就决心不再相信外人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.01,0:17:14.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后一定还会流更多的血吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.98,0:17:17.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.93,0:17:19.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次我一定不会让悲剧重演
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.96,0:17:25.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.11,0:17:26.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.74,0:17:29.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候蒂安也要和我们一起哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.15,0:17:33.32,Gurakiesu,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是群天真的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.78,0:17:35.40,Gurakiesu,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那和我们没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.96,0:17:37.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法姆？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.93,0:17:39.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞行大赛  蒂安也
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.69,0:17:42.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法姆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.59,0:17:43.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样  要参加吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.02,0:17:45.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快决定
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.58,0:17:46.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法姆  快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.42,0:17:53.59,Gurakiesu,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你  你们…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.93,0:17:56.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还真动手了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.31,0:17:59.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中招的是我  所以法姆…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.49,0:18:04.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒂安  一决胜负吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.82,0:18:11.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我赢了的话  就要一起参加飞行大赛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.16,0:18:29.33,Gurakiesu,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…她没浮上来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.98,0:18:31.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没浮上来是指？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.40,0:18:31.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法姆！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.25,0:18:34.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法姆…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.55,0:18:41.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燃料  冷却液  克劳迪亚没有问题
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.88,0:18:44.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高度计  调整陀螺仪  控制器没有问题
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.72,0:18:46.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,启动前检查一切正常
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.30,0:18:48.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白  点火
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.70,0:18:57.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要坐坐看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.31,0:19:01.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个给你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.04,0:19:04.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机体飞起来后就要调整节流阀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.36,0:19:04.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个也给你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.06,0:19:05.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要将节流阀开到底
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.46,0:19:08.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得形象点
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.26,0:19:12.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是低下头然后一边前进一边上升
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.26,0:19:16.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是第一次飞行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.44,0:19:18.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和平常一样就行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.02,0:19:19.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提高动力
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.82,0:19:40.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,节流阀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.87,0:19:42.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把节流阀开到底
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.96,0:19:48.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒂安
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.27,0:20:03.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真浪费燃料
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.74,0:20:09.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒂安  快看
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.81,0:20:20.32,Gurakiesu,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是风吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.35,0:20:49.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒂安  谢谢你帮助我们
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.26,0:21:00.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒂安小姐她说了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.53,0:21:04.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她说我们应该不会再见面了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.35,0:21:08.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊  说得真凄凉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.93,0:21:10.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但她还说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.10,0:21:12.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望有一天
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.96,0:21:16.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们还能在同一片天空下飞翔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.65,0:21:24.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路斯基尼亚很快就会出现在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.60,0:21:26.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离开格拉吉艾斯后
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.10,0:21:27.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们去找希尔维乌斯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.65,0:21:31.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后去救莉莉陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.02,0:21:38.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,10点钟方向  出现多支舰队
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.33,0:21:40.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然有这么多
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.18,0:21:45.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是主力舰队…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.54,0:21:47.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是联邦的舰队吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.31,0:21:51.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是  虽然打着联邦的旗帜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.72,0:21:52.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.36,0:21:55.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莱图斯  塔·奥比斯丹  凯奥斯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.71,0:22:03.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,联邦的主力舰队正在…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.51,0:22:13.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么塔·奥比斯丹和凯奥斯的舰队会…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.46,0:22:15.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法姆
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.84,0:22:20.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.54,0:22:22.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只是诱饵
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.78,0:22:26.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得快点告诉蒂安
